  # Customer Segment Analysis
  
  Customer segmentation metrics for targeted marketing.
  
  ## Metrics per Segment:
  - Customer Count
  - Total Orders
  - Total Revenue
  - Average Order Value
  - Active Customers (Last 30 Days)
  - Customer Share (%)
  - Revenue Share (%)
  
  ## Use Cases:
  - Identify high-value segments
  - Target marketing campaigns
  - Customer retention strategies
  - Segment-specific pricing
}
